{"tid":1816434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣戰線對香港真係好重要","createTime":"2020-01-08T08:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T00:26:10.000Z","uid":326800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"87fdf5dc53ba9cdc2c88a552a78d908f87688f59","tid":1816434,"uid":326800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"唔知各位身邊有幾多台灣朋友，可能唔多，但一、兩個總有掛？<br />\n呢幾日無論點都好，都要提醒、鼓勵、支持佢地去投票。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文真係絕對唔可以輸！<br />\n試諗下，而家有幾多手足暫避、流亡左去台灣，有線、鏗鏘集都已經講過。<br />\n如果選上的唔係蔡英文，佢地的處境會變得更加危險，而且<span style=\"color: red;\">一定</span>會被清算...<br />\n佢地付出既已經太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返唔到屋企，喺台灣仲可以有人幫，我地又可以做到幾多黎幫佢地？<br />\n<br />\n可能台灣朋友唔會睇連登，但facebook呢？ig呢？<br />\n簡單D，可能直接分享影片再等台灣朋友spread開去已經幫到！！<br />\n<br />\n《大聲說話》係蔡英文的競選影片，有台灣團隊做了對比香港畫面的影片 （未睇快D睇，同share！！）<br />\n<br />\n〈大聲說話-兩個世界版〉Youtube連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ykcVIQMrc4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FykcVIQMrc4A&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6Ij2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=d2bf6fd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ykcVIQMrc4A</a><br />\n<br />\nfrom FB專頁「辣台派wajinpie」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WAJINPIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWAJINPIE%2F&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6Ij2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=30b5ef0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WAJINPIE/</a>"},{"pid":"9e8e4a29a2edd3977e1ef8ec7e3de400b42e327b","tid":1816434,"uid":326800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:00:18.000Z","msg":"加埋今日appledaily<br />\n<br />\n【台灣選戰】<br />\n蔡英文競選廣告併反送中畫面重剪 《紐時》記者：史上最強<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200108/60462155?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2QXE6p425wAfb9iJ69G7lt0Sza5f-iafbX7cYNkCCuexF_cFSJtKtcVro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2F